{"tid":2261004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［12港人送中］中國司法局下禁令律師不准接案","createTime":"2020-10-28T04:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T07:37:12.000Z","uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3845b4d1d6182a2953d5bf7c3ec80f2b2b33d926","tid":2261004,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"12港人送中 中國司法局硬上弓 下禁令律師不准接案「已代理的必須解除」<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果日報】12名涉反修例案件的港青疑在潛逃往台灣時被中國海警截獲，被秘密關押67日，事件已在國際引起廣泛關注。12名港人的家屬至今都對親人的情況一無所知，而且他們委託的律師也未能見到當事人，甚至有律師所屬的律師樓接到司法局的禁令，不准他們繼續協助被捕港人，「已代理的必須要解除」。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#陽光司法 #貪贓枉法<br />\n#不斷施壓 #政治打壓<br />\n#save12hkyouths #願平安歸手足<br />\n#20201028新聞"},{"pid":"f2e259b1231faca7c8c42bbbda332201e7d01188","tid":2261004,"uid":4043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:23:09.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"e968ca9dbf3845e6d4272d4d6282626a80462a28","tid":2261004,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45337d1d5fc39fb10363868da82a4bfb70a0ee4","tid":2261004,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"中共已經完全唔理國際睇法，好嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacfe65b940e7c231841284d919787dd3ea1c11e","tid":2261004,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3f6d47c0dd64dbdc90fc85df95ed1a69739db3","tid":2261004,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c0a0f8a79ec995880f848dad5b40156e3bac340","tid":2261004,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:26:58.000Z","msg